OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776791154
OL,3,CArmed men who stabbed three people
OL,4,Csentenced after being run into by car
OL,6,FJones was sentenced to 15 years in
OL,7,Fprison, with a four-year extended
OL,8,Flicence period, while Wlazlo was
OL,9,Fsentenced for 13 years, also with a
OL,10,Ffour-year extended licence period .
OL,12,FThe court heard the pair first went to
OL,13,Fa residential address in Bentilee,
OL,14,Flooking for someone called "Salty'".
OL,16,FAfter finding that he was not in, they
OL,17,Fslashed his brother's arm and "a
OL,18,Ffurther swing was taken at him".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776791154
OL,3,CArmed men who stabbed three people
OL,4,Csentenced after being run into by car
OL,6,FLess than five minutes later, they
OL,7,Fstopped a car and attempted to stab a
OL,8,Fman in the passenger's seat.
OL,10,FWlazlo grabbed the driver by the hair
OL,11,Fand tried to pull her out the car.
OL,13,FShe managed to get out, but Jones
OL,14,Fdrove a motorbike towards her, while
OL,15,FWlazlo kicked her to the ground.
OL,17,FThree hours later, the pair went to
OL,18,FGalsworthy Road and stabbed a man in
OL,19,Fthe thigh.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776791154
OL,3,CArmed men who stabbed three people
OL,4,Csentenced after being run into by car
OL,6,FThey then went to Dean Place, where
OL,7,Fthey smashed the windows, armed with a
OL,8,Fmachete and a pistol.
OL,10,FWlazlo shot through the front window,
OL,11,Fwhen a car ran the pair over in an
OL,12,Fattempt to stop them.
OL,14,FStaffordshire Police released CCTV
OL,15,Ffootage of the moment they were run
OL,16,Fover.
OL,18,FJones is seen riding a motorcycle when
OL,19,Fthe vehicle collides with him, while
OL,20,FWlazlo - who is also on a bike - is
OL,21,Fran over on a driveway.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
