PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776791154
OL,3,CArmed men who stabbed three people
OL,4,Csentenced after being run into by car
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"Looking for "Salty"
OL,13,FAddressing Jones, Judge McConaghy
OL,14,Fsaid: "On March 28, 2025 when you
OL,15,Fattended a residential address looking
OL,16,Ffor someone called 'Salty', he wasn't
OL,17,Fin but when the door opened you swung
OL,18,Fa kitchen knife at his brother
OL,19,Fslashing his arm and a further swing
OL,20,Fwas taken at him despite already being
OL,21,Fwounded.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776791154
OL,3,CArmed men who stabbed three people
OL,4,Csentenced after being run into by car
OL,6,F"Less than five minutes later you
OL,7,Fimpeded a car driven by a woman
OL,8,Flooking for Salty. You opened the
OL,9,Fdriver's side and reached over trying
OL,10,Fto stab a man in the face and he ran
OL,11,Faway."
OL,13,FThe judge added: "You, Wlazlo, grabbed
OL,14,Fthe woman by the hair and tried to
OL,15,Fpull her out of the car, she managed
OL,16,Fto climb across to the passenger side
OL,17,Fand got out, and you, Jones, drove a
OL,18,Fmotorbike towards her, and then you,
OL,19,FWlazlo, kicked her to the ground.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776791154
OL,3,CArmed men who stabbed three people
OL,4,Csentenced after being run into by car
OL,6,F"Three hours later you went to
OL,7,FGalsworthy Road and you stabbed a man
OL,8,Fin the thigh. From there you went to
OL,9,FDean Place where you smashed the
OL,10,Fwindows armed with a machete and a
OL,11,Fpistol, which you, Wlazlo, shot
OL,12,Fthrough the front window of the
OL,13,Foccupied property, and a car turned in
OL,14,Fand ran over you both to stop you from
OL,15,Fbehaving in the way you were.
OL,17,F"After that you, Wlazlo, were talking
OL,18,Fabout getting your shotgun to kill the
OL,19,Fpeople who'd just run you over, and
OL,20,FJones you fled the area."
OL,26,@nD@AOU|D@YO]
